语法: 数据类型 变量名 = 数值/变量</p>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token comment">// 将10赋值给num</span>
<span class="token keyword">int</span> num <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">10</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
