</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>代码开始执行,线程 A 和线程 B 开始抢占线程,当 A 抢占成功,进入 TimeLock,reentrantLock.tryLock(3, TimeUnit.SECONDS)此时为 true,三秒内能够上锁,此时线程 A 打印 get lock 并且将线程休眠 5 秒,此时线程 B 进入 TimeLock,但是此时进程已经休眠 5s 小于 3s,reentrantLock.tryLock(3, TimeUnit.SECONDS)三秒内无法上锁,reentrantLock.tryLock(3, TimeUnit.SECONDS)为 false,打印 not get lock 并抛出错误</p>
